        "action": "Introduce specific penalties for middle and outer lane hogging on the motorway",
        "additional_details": "I think it's extremely dangerous when there are people sitting in the outer lanes of the motorway when there's nothing in the inner lanes.",
        "background": "I want the Government to introduce specific penalties for people who persistently hog the middle and outer lanes on the motorway. They should get fined or points for this.",
